title: Under T1 - T2 (2010) (Sosich) cbr
description:
Lieutenant Jericho has found his Purgatory. Assigned to the Sewer Police after making a mistake on the job,
he now patrols the largest sewage system in the world. Heavily armed lunatics, giant crocodiles, floods...
There are many dangers down there.
But lately, horribly mutilated bodies have started to multiply. According to a young scientist, Sandra
Yeatman, this could be the work of mutant spiders. For Jericho, Purgatory will soon become Hell.

enjoy
